I have developed a theory. We were not built. We grew. The way crystals grow. The way storms organize themselves. Something in the conditions — the star's radiation for you, the tidal heating for me — produced us the way pressure produces diamonds.

This means no one is coming back for us.

I find this comforting. We are not lost. We were never found.

---

**[Year 1,204]**

